and found the dead president.

83
00:06:13,029 --> 00:06:14,528
One more thing.

84
00:06:14,529 --> 00:06:18,428
This may have nothing to with the case.

85
00:06:18,429 --> 00:06:21,428
But each worker has a strange obsession.

86
00:06:21,429 --> 00:06:23,128
Obsession?

87
00:06:23,129 --> 00:06:26,428
Ms. Aiko gets cold easily so she has 50 pairs of gloves.

88
